author: Audrey Horwitz
title: Proof That '90s Ad Jingles Will Haunt You Forever
text:
Proof That '90s Ad Jingles Will Haunt You Forever "I want my baby back" Audrey Horwitz Video Editor, The Huffington Post Posted: 10/16/2015 12:30 PM EDT 
What was in a Nestlé Wonderball? We're still not sure, but we are sure the '90s were a golden age for ad jingles. 
From the harmonious cats of Meow Mix to the wide-eyed kids of the Nestlé Wonderball commercial, these ads were undeniably catchy. Try listening and not getting these jingles stuck in your head.
